SubjectRegistered Products Regulations
PrecisREGISTERED PRODUCTS REGULATIONS, in order to define the type of registered products covered (e.g., registered retirement savings plans, registered education savings plans, tax free savings accounts) and to specify that disclosed information must be provided in a language and manner that is clear and simple, and not misleading.
